{"tid":1624661,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係網傳斷手fa","createTime":"2019-10-05T04:31:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T05:02:46.000Z","uid":330646,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fc36e01593b405067272c1121fc32aac2a57cbc2","tid":1624661,"uid":330646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:31:02.000Z","msg":"（代傳）<br />\n<br />\n首先，想同大家講一聲對唔住！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n岀咗院後無即時岀黎報平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為打咗好多枝止痛針，止嘔針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要幾日無食過嘢同飲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身體有少少虛弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但尋日岀咗院，今朝先算係行得企得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家諒解<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然岀院後我已經見咗傳媒，希望大家知我無事，但今日都企岀嚟同大家報個平安<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好再擔心我，我手無斷，我無被失蹤，我岀咗院，依加排咗期等照胃鏡<br />\n<br />\n其次，我係留院期間，完全接收唔到外界資訊，我無擔心過自己安全，無擔心會唔會起訴我，反而係好想知岀面情況，我好擔心大家嘅安全，好擔心有無人受傷，香港人，可唔可以應承我，唔好令自己受傷！唔好俾自己有事！！！我真係好擔心大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於有無係拘留期間受不人道對待，我已經同傳媒反映咗，大家唔洗擔心<br />\n<br />\n另外，其實警隊有好多好警察，有警員知我情況唔太好，係移交咗我之後，專登返嚟問我情況，亦有好多友善嘅社區警員（真心希望大家明白我點解咁講)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此外，亦希望大家可以搵到我被捕前後嘅片，証明我無仼何衝擊動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，個樣好殘，只係唔想見樣，想點fact check ，你地話事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bde5b81791efdfbcf19f2d4610c0786738dccc9","tid":1624661,"uid":330646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:34:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54ce22dd6605c14abc338aaebdfe4d1c7704e776","tid":1624661,"uid":330646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:34:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91eddf56ec0a6b261343fb3bc06111f7dabd5783","tid":1624661,"uid":330646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:34:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"507e3d9451b9db7e8ee1cbc4ff503b36dd5822a0","tid":1624661,"uid":330646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:34:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a53efc851fc94cd599c291cb36955f2276c9eefd","tid":1624661,"uid":330646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:35:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f02e336f34d2a0e4a1a4257068f340aae87a1f7","tid":1624661,"uid":330646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:35:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7a853ad3866800c4edc78b2dc5756e6cc1d52bc","tid":1624661,"uid":330646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:35:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98665ae76a35ac186e496a4cc4e370c2e4af7107","tid":1624661,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:35:25.000Z","msg":"越睇越唔對路"},{"pid":"95295038120eae8e6c3ca5490c808ad6c9ff76d7","tid":1624661,"uid":330646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:35:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a6d2e77f6cdb9c620bbed7bd07d7efe6efd2074","tid":1624661,"uid":330646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:36:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aea8f3c2210c569b715016145a11469f0e6fb119","tid":1624661,"uid":330646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:37:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7de075db6d1f26e08ebf01459ac32ec3c618fb7b","tid":1624661,"uid":265133,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:02:46.000Z","msg":"報平安唔係甘報 同我求其打段字話自己係831死者報訊一樣"}]}